==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪlt|-ɪlt]]

===Noun===
'''stilt''' (''plural'' '''stilts''')

# Either of two [[pole]]s with footrests that allow someone to stand or walk above the ground; used mostly by [[entertainer]]s.
# A tall [[pillar]] or [[post]] used to support some [[structure]]; often above [[water]].
# Any of various [[wading bird]]s of the genera ''[[Himantopus]]'' and ''[[Cladorhynchus]]'', related to the [[avocet]], that have extremely long legs and long thin [[bill]]s.

